And yet manie of these, like the rauenous fowles, of all other are the leanest: they catch all, and can keepe nothing: for the Lord bloweth vpon it, and as Namans leprosie with his gift cleaued to Gehesi;
               Hagg ai. 1.7 so GODS curse with his portion adhaereth to them likewise.
